---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Landscaping Services in Las Cruces, NM | Brainard's Greenscapes"
description: "Full-service landscaping, hardscaping, xeriscaping, irrigation, and maintenance in Las Cruces, NM. Free estimates from Brainard's Greenscapes."
---
<section class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Services</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">From design to installation to ongoing care — everything your landscape needs, built for the Las Cruces climate.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% for service in services %}
      <a href="{{ service.url }}" class="group relative block bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-green-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/assets/images/BG_logo_tree_only.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 transition-opacity watermark" loading="lazy">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-green-700">{{ service.title }}</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">{{ service.description }}</p>
        <span class="text-green-700 text-sm font-medium">{{ service.linkText }} &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% include "partials/banner.njk" %}
